'''马西劳'''（'''Mesilau'''）为[[婆罗洲|婆罗洲]][[沙巴|沙巴]][[基纳巴卢国家公园|基纳巴卢国家公园]][[基纳巴卢山|基纳巴卢山]]东部山脊高原及周边地区。马西劳是唯一一个普通游客可到达的[[马来王猪笼草|马来王猪笼草]]（{{small|''Nepenthes rajah''}}）分布地。<ref name=Sabah>Clarke, C.M. 2001. ''[[沙巴的猪笼草指南|A Guide to the Pitcher Plants of Sabah]]''. Natural History Publications (Borneo), Kota Kinabalu.</ref>每天，由导致带领游客有组织的去往“猪笼草园”参观。该景点收费，营业时间为每天的早上9时至下午4时。<ref>[http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2011/06/12/chilling-out-a-tropical-destination.html Chilling out in a tropical destination] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160523124237/http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2011/06/12/chilling-out-a-tropical-destination.html |date=2016-05-23 }}. ''The Jakarta Post'', June 12, 2011.</ref>

东马西劳河（{{small|Mesilau East River}}）和西马西劳河（{{small|Mesilau West River}}）从马西劳地区中穿过。<ref name=Kurata>Kurata, S. 1976. ''[[基纳巴卢山的猪笼草|Nepenthes of Mount Kinabalu]]''. Sabah National Parks Publications No. 2, Sabah National Parks Trustees, Kota Kinabalu.</ref>东马西劳河具一个深沟<ref>Allen, E.F. 1971. {{PDFlink|[http://www.vireya.net/archive/AllenRHS71.pdf Collecting and Growing Sabah Rhododendrons.]}} In: ''Rhododendron and Camellia Year Book 1971''. Royal Horticultural Society, London.</ref>，马西劳洞（{{small|Mesilau Cave}}）位于其附近。<ref name=Kurata />

去往基纳巴卢山的两条路线之一起始于马西劳自然度假村，其被称为马西劳步道（{{small|Mesilau Trail}}）。马西劳线在[[拉央-拉央|拉央-拉央]]附近与基纳巴卢峰线汇合，交汇点海拔约2700米。<ref>Thong, J. 2006. {{PDFlink|[http://www.vcps.au.com/journals/81_Sep_2006Public.pdf Travels around North Borneo – Part 1.]}} ''[[维多利亚食虫植物协会杂志|Victorian Carnivorous Plant Society Journal]]'' '''81''': 12–17.</ref>

